TEXT.S: = Takubuwan = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Hwareynsu ka alang Takubuwan. 451 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 1,209 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 17% niqan 211 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 83% niqan 998 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis 13%, Sakizaya 3%, Truku 1%.
